    "macroSummary": "Trump's hawkish Iran address has triggered classic risk-off flows with oil spiking above $100 (activating stagflation watch), dollar surging on safe haven demand, and risk assets selling off. The geopolitical escalation adds a new layer of complexity to an already fragile macro environment, potentially accelerating the transition from oversold relief rally back to full bear market dynamics.",
