      "Monitor BMNR cash-secured puts closely as Bitcoin selling pressure from whales and continued retreat toward $62,300 structural level creates favorable entry opportunities",
      "Consider expanding short book exposure as relief rally thesis weakens with geopolitical risk overlay and stagflationary oil spike",
      "Maintain Maturity sector overweight as defensive positioning proves prescient amid renewed risk-off environment and rising bond yields"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
